Four-step garage quote
With the Auda-Taller tool, Audatex ensures that the user gets a quote in just four steps: identifying the vehicle, searching for the spare part, creating a quote and generating it.
Ease of use is an essential component of these systems, especially in order to convince older professionals who, to a greater or lesser extent, are reactive to the use of new management techniques.
